        dct:source narr:Sample_1MvpV2ConcisionOneProductRulings ;
        narr:theme "Sales and fundraising demos need vivid, functional renders of the product experience, not fully constructed features — clear, smooth, and valuable outranks finished, and simplification is the operative discipline." ;
